b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2865,"category_name":"Updates","pr_category_id":"2","title_name":"Version Update [Update]","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1645758000\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>As a token of our appreciation, the following item has been sent to players who started playing before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1645758000\\"><\/span>.<br><br>\\u30fbTenfold Summon Voucher &times; 1<br><br>This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after reception. If the gift isn&#39;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>Version 2.17.0 will be available for download around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1645671600\\"><\/span>. You may install it when it becomes available; otherwise, an automatic update will occur around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1645758000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>When you update to version 2.17.0 and play co-op, you will no longer be matched with players using earlier versions of the game. Rooms created by players using earlier versions will not display in the Room List, and you will not be able to join them using Find a Room, Join Nearby Players, Enter an ID, or alliance chat.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>To celebrate the update, we&#39;ll be sending all players a Tenfold Summon Voucher after the automatic update. This notice will be updated after it has been distributed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Note: The Tenfold Summon Voucher will not be distributed until after the automatic update, even if you complete the update to version 2.17.0 early.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Update Details<\/div><div>\\u30fbBalance adjustments will be made to the Kaleidoscape on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1646373600\\"><\/span>. For further details, please see the corresponding in-game notification upon its release.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe Blessed Bloodline and A Dazzling Defense onslaught events will be added to the event compendium on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1646028000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe adventurer Gala Emile&#39;s adventurer skin may be unlocked in the Alberian Battle Royale starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1646028000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbSupport for upcoming adventurers and quests scheduled to appear in late February through March will be added and certain unresolved issues will be addressed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Other Changes<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe order in which enemies perform certain actions in Iblis&#39;s Trial (Water) and Iblis&#39;s Trial (Shadow) in Trials of the Mighty will be adjusted.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Issues Addressed<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhile playing the Kaleidoscape with the adventurer Mega Man, his skill gauge will neither charge automatically nor be fully charged after moving to another floor.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhile playing the Kaleidoscape, certain adventurers may get stuck on objects on the map and become unable to move. (This issue will be resolved by adjusting the location of these objects.)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. It may take time for the store to reflect the updated information. Players may not be able to perform updates due to their device&#39;s data cache being full. If you are unable to perform the update, restart your device, and then try downloading it from the store.<\/div><div>2. Any adventurers and game screenshots shown are still in development.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1645066800,"prev_article_id":"2780","next_article_id":"2914","image_path":"","update_time":1645757948}}}'